com.tractrac.model.lib.api

Class AbstractModelTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • junit.framework.Assert
      • junit.framework.TestCase
        • com.tractrac.model.lib.api.AbstractModelTest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    junit.framework.Test
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractSubscriptionTest

    public abstract class AbstractModelTest
extends junit.framework.TestCase

    Abstract class that can be inherited for the test classes. It has utility methods to create mock objects that are used by the test classes in order to create a model of objects for testing

    See Also:
    Mock Object
